======
PGSync
======

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pgsync.svg
   :target: https://pypi.org/project/pgsync/
   :alt: PyPI Version

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/pgsync.svg
